    "body": "hi @helderjnpinto, I've merged this change into the Besu main branch. So can test with the Besu dev build. It can be used similarly to other transitions https://besu.hyperledger.org/en/latest/HowTo/Configure/Consensus-Protocols/Add-Validators/#adding-and-removing-validators-without-voting\r\n\r\nExample configuration for ibft2 to change the block period to 4 seconds at block 1240 would be:\r\n```\r\n\"transitions\": {\r\n\t\"ibft2\": [\r\n\t\t{\r\n\t\t\t\"block\": 1240,\r\n\t\t\t\"blockperiodseconds\": 4\r\n\t\t}\r\n\t]\r\n}\r\n```",
